title: Stadionul Clinceni
text: Stadionul Clinceni is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Clinceni">Clinceni</a>, <a href="Romania">Romania</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home ground of <a href="FC%20Academica%20Clinceni">Academica Clinceni</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 4,500 seats.
